Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}A stubborn maintenance worker, Whitman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}A last locomotive, the No. 825...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}On their home world, a searing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}steam whistle echoes out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Next time on Tales of the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways, Episode 8:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Afterglow"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}We're going to encounter\N{\c&He1e1e1&}something at the next station.{\i0}